{"tid":706470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大阪6.1級淺層地震 至少兩死多人傷 有房屋大火","createTime":"2018-06-18T02:13:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-18T03:00:57.000Z","uid":60545,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f4997fc78eeb8b9051ffc9e2d2d10aad462db671","tid":706470,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T02:13:29.000Z","msg":"日本大阪府北部發生6.1級地震，當地電視台報道，最少2人死亡，數人受傷，已送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n地震導致部分建築物外牆受損，屋頂瓦片跌到地上。有房屋起火並「燒通頂」，消防向火場灑水。有居民報稱有水管破裂，湧出水柱。部分民眾走到空地暫避。<br />\n<br />\n地震發生在當地早上7時58分左右，震央位於大阪府北部，震源深度10公里。大阪附近及關西地區大範圍有震感，部分地區停電，暫時沒有海嘯。<br />\n<br />\n新幹線、跨區鐵路及地鐵，部分服務暫停。區內3個機場，在地震後暫停飛機升降，機場人員檢查跑道受損情況，航空服務目前已經恢復。附近福井縣有官員說，當地15座核反應堆，運作正常。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1402258-20180618.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1402258-20180618.htm&d=jdNRKCjb3sKG7K77ecYh1ACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=dd11fc25\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1402258-20180618.htm&h=3a8eea4a\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1402258-20180618.htm</a>"},{"pid":"ff0ae08427f14c8d15ab385611570c3915f3a028","tid":706470,"uid":4661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T02:16:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b62702fab9efebca59ba8cf2e11ba27eb10a0b5","tid":706470,"uid":156108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T02:23:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"186bed3a09efda3acdf1368a6d89c96ac790a914","tid":706470,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T02:24:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4699542116dc93cb3dab646bc76f2176482fb3e","tid":706470,"uid":163350,"like":0,"dislike":21,"score":-21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T02:26:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a0046cbbb6aa27264b8c85ae894ec13ca9ed5e47","tid":706470,"uid":69886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T02:27:48.000Z","msg":"係咪死既都係香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bdc704f0c8876da134e3056a470b0740aac6ddc","tid":706470,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T02:33:12.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36a73da565d97fb822c952b2458d15393454a282","tid":706470,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T02:40:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c0c779901bbd80c1a7f938d42f896e45454a1407","tid":706470,"uid":93479,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T02:45:34.000Z","msg":"衛冕冠軍德國今晨意外不敵墨西哥，令球迷大跌眼鏡。而在墨西哥，群眾在夏榮羅辛奴入球時歡喜若狂，更錄得「人為地震」。<br />\n<br />\n雖說墨西哥位處環太平洋地震帶，但當地負責監測地震的組織指墨西哥早上11時32分有「最少兩個監測站錄得地殼活動」，稱「很可能是群眾密集彈跳而造成」。當時正是墨西哥翼鋒夏榮羅辛奴入球的時間，最終墨西哥亦以此入球爆冷贏波。<br />\n<br />\n球迷慶祝引發人為地震過去亦曾有發生。秘魯今屆是36年來首度參戰世界盃，去年主將法芬對紐西蘭的入球曾引發這南美國家錄得黎克特制1級的小地震；去年巴塞隆拿歐聯奇蹟反勝巴黎聖日耳門亦有類似情況。<br />\n<br />\n跳丫跳丫，出事啦依家！"},{"pid":"edffc99c85a30f0122929a697dd71317c61ea0f3","tid":706470,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T02:49:06.000Z","msg":"福氣"},{"pid":"25efb966a7f0edd23deef4718134fb9e9521879e","tid":706470,"uid":29929,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T02:54:35.000Z","msg":"典解唔係港豬死"},{"pid":"22b7906c63fe172c1ea1aa14a0cbce3350a396cd","tid":706470,"uid":88309,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T03:00:57.000Z","msg":"睇到另一個post啲人<br />\n仲好意思話當地人睇落都冇嘢，仲好意思話買咗fastpass問人usj開唔開，大佬，人地幾十年黎都住喺地震國家，唔通佢地做咗準備又會同你地講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\"